# AXIOM validator seed list — bootstrap addresses for fresh
# wallet installs. Community-maintained: PR against axiom-dist to
# add / retire entries. Wallets fetch this on first launch and
# discover the rest of the network via gossip.
#
# Format: name<TAB>address<TAB>email
# Address column = validator's SMTP host (currently unused; Kiddo
# opens SMTP, not the wallet).
alpha	172.20.0.42	alpha@axiom
beta	172.20.0.42	beta@axiom
gamma	172.20.0.42	gamma@axiom
delta	172.20.0.42	delta@axiom
epsilon	172.20.0.42	epsilon@axiom
zeta	172.20.0.42	zeta@axiom
eta	172.20.0.42	eta@axiom
theta	172.20.0.42	theta@axiom
iota	172.20.0.42	iota@axiom
kappa	172.20.0.42	kappa@axiom
